156
00:11:37,581 --> 00:11:39,152
Aku akan dipecat, tepatnya.

157
00:11:40,122 --> 00:11:41,522
Maksud kamu apa?

158
00:11:42,652 --> 00:11:43,851
Aku...

159
00:11:44,762 --> 00:11:47,292
membiarkan Jang Seon Ho jatuh dan mati.

160
00:11:47,961 --> 00:11:49,731
